<FILEID>AP-NR-10-20-89 0316EDT</FILEID>
<FIRST>r p VirginiaGovernor     10-20 0410</FIRST>
<SECOND>Virginia Governor,0423</SECOND>
<HEAD>Virginia Gubernatorial Candidates Spar Over Civil Rights Leader</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: RETRANSMITTING to fix slugline.</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By JOE TAYLOR</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>RICHMOND, Va. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A man seeking to become the nation's first
