<HEAD>Soviets Offer to Send Doctors, Geologists, Rescuers to California</HEAD>
<HEAD>With AM-SF Quake, Bjt</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MOSCOW (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The Soviet government is offering to send doctors,
geologists and rescue workers to Northern California to help with
earthquake relief, Tass reported Friday.
   The Health Ministry is willing to send trauma specialists and
surgeons to the earthquake area and the Geology Ministry is
offering experts with their own equipment to help with seismic
