<HEAD>FBI Agent Stabbed On Street</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   An FBI agent received a minor stab wound
Friday when a homeless man apparently attacked him at random,
police said.
   Chris Warrener was attacked after his wife, Gayla, who also is
an FBI agent, was bumped by a man as she was returning to her car
after lunch with her husband in downtown Washignton.
   Mrs. Warrener called to her husband for help after being bumped
by the man, a scuffle followed, and Warrener was stabbed in the
